  "name": "RPlog_A_N_kosi_Meets_a_Chief",
  "title": "A N'kosi Meets a Chief",
  "summary": "In a conference room of the New Republic government complex on Ord Mantell, Fleet liaison Commander Rasi convenes a meeting between Chief of State Leia Organa Solo, Senator Tokoga of Mon Calamari, and the Horansi leader K'tyyri Tarashabi to discuss the plight of her CSA-occupied homeworld, Mutanda. After her rambunctious cubs Sufa and Yadumu are escorted off by a Wookiee and the protocol droid C-3PO, K'tyyri -- former Mbwana and acting N'kosi -- recounts the long, bloody war on Mutanda against the CSA, Griffon Alliance, and Empire, and the eventual capture and humiliation of her family before they fled to Caspar. Leia and Tokoga pledge that the Republic seeks only to help free Mutanda without imposing membership or interfering in Horansi culture, and they agree the first step is slipping an envoy onto the planet to speak with the fief leaders. K'tyyri offers to guide them and rally loyal fiefs once the CSA threat is lifted, and the meeting ends with the parties in agreement, quarters arranged for K'tyyri and her cubs, and plans to reconvene after the Republic's advisors weigh in.",
